data.description: This home is in the city limits and nestled on a hill with panoramic views of the city.  Beautiful sunsets and sunrises create a picturesque setting.  Brick construction with Austin stone accents, providing a classic and durable exterior.  Large corner lot for added space and privacy.  Extra-large driveway with an additional half circle for ample parking.  Large back patio featuring an outdoor kitchen with a stone and granite bar.  The pergola enhances the outdoor ambiance.  Landscaping with boulders, crushed granite river rock, mature trees, and shrubs for a natural and aesthetically pleasing environment. Beautiful stone and brick archway entry, creating an impressive first impression.  Mahogany wood sculpted ceiling and accents, add warmth and elegance. Brick and stone fireplace with a wooden mantel, creating a cozy focal point.  Kitchen island with a granite countertop, offering both functionality and style.  Granite throughout the home provides a luxurious and cohesive design.  Great room with a vaulted ceiling and wooden beams, enhancing the sense of space and character.  Large yard, providing outdoor space for various activities.  Three-car garage, offering convenience and ample parking and storage.
